This project aims to help SchroDog2 win the game in Sommoner's Rift.

# Riot API
`API_KEY` is stored as an environment variable in `.env` file. The developer api key 
can be fetched from https://developer.riotgames.com/. The rate limit is set as
- 20 requests every 1 seconds(s)
- 100 requests every 2 minutes(s)

Developer's page: https://developer.riotgames.com/apis#match-v5/GET_getMatch

# Datbase
Data is stored in `db/match.db` as a sqlite databse. The database could also be 
connected from console using command `sqlite3 db\match.db`

# Use Case
1. Find teams that have highest/lowest win rates

# Contirbute
If you want to contribute, create a branch and send the merge request! Any interesting ideas are welcome.
